name: Kebun Warung
address: H28H+XM2, Belimbing, Pupuan, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Looking for a few days of down time in the rice fields of Bali? Kebun Villas gorgeous gardens, a crystal clear swimming pool  quirky antiques and friendly, local service make this the perfect place to relax.  Use their bikes to tour through nearby villages, and have lunch a few KM north at Warung Dedy serving delicious Balinese coconut-chicken soup.  Ask the owner to borrow her binoculars and bird book, and see if you can spot kingfisher and eagles!  Short day trips to the white sleeping Buddha and the local beach can fill a few days.  A great value, too!
review 2: Perfect place to relax. We got caught in the rain, perfect home to wsit it out, no pressure, just peace.
review 3: Great place with very kind staff and an amazing view
